Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.03,0:01:38.28,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs36\bord4\blur4\fax0.18\fad(655,554)\pos(700,541)}The Jinchuuriki Tears
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.17,0:01:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a Paper Bomb left here, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.55,0:02:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a type that explodes the instant it's peeled off...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.18,0:02:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll just have to detonate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.10,0:02:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.14,0:02:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We're detonating a Paper Bomb!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.93,0:02:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop working and take cover!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.36,0:02:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.91,0:02:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Now isn't the time to be discussing candidates for a new Kazekage!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.62,0:02:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you think about the worst-case scenario,\Nisn't it important to seize the initiative?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.42,0:02:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly, the plan to rescue\NLord Kazekage should be the priority!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.21,0:02:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Securing village safety is what's important!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.09,0:02:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We must not break up our limited forces in conditions like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.64,0:02:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.06,0:02:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.98,0:02:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Reporting!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.44,0:02:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,An enemy trap has been discovered in the rubble blocking the entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.94,0:02:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We are currently proceeding with its detonation...\NThere have been no casualties.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.86,0:03:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,However, a portion of the entrance collapsed due to the effects of the explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.03,0:03:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems it will take an extra half day for repairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.54,0:03:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it. Arrange it so that those who are available are dispatched to the repair site immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.96,0:03:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.30,0:03:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.06,0:03:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thanks to Gaara, the Village Hidden in the Sand was left almost completely undamaged...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.15,0:03:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But... we paid too great a price for that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.20,0:03:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Reporting!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.03,0:03:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,All of the bodies of those guarding the skies have been verified.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.91,0:03:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,There is probably little doubt that the enemy infiltrated
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.33,0:03:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,the center of the village from the sky...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.83,0:03:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.25,0:03:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.21,0:03:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We have been contacted by the tracking unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.46,0:04:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Kankuro was discovered about half a day out of the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.59,0:04:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He is unconscious and in serious condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.93,0:04:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kankuro...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.52,0:04:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Some members of the tracking unit have recovered Kankuro and his puppets.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.35,0:04:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,They are on their way back to the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.65,0:04:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the location of Lord Kazekage?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.78,0:04:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The remaining members of the tracking unit are in pursuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.57,0:04:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,There should be a report soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.91,0:04:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You're late, Sasori...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.58,0:04:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you didn't like to keep people waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.71,0:04:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But... I had enough fun to make up for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.84,0:04:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.93,0:04:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get so touchy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.85,0:04:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You secured your mission target, the One-Tail, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.64,0:05:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,My mission comes next... after taking care of this guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.69,0:05:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But the one you're after...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.61,0:05:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I still don't know where he is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.78,0:05:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be easier if he'd just come to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.04,0:05:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.29,0:05:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of Jinchuuriki was he again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.71,0:05:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, worst case scenario, even if I can't find him...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.38,0:05:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,...nobody can complain since we caught one of the Jinchuuriki.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.31,0:05:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Gaara, we're coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.40,0:05:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto! I know you're in a hurry,\Nbut don't disrupt the unit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.90,0:05:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.36,0:05:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't lose your cool...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.03,0:05:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Jiraiya told you not to, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.33,0:05:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,For crying out loud...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.62,0:05:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Temari!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.59,0:06:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and get him to the operating room!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.43,0:06:10.34,Title,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\fs30\c&H755F5A&\fax0.08\frx18\fry338\bord0\frz17.953\t(647,780,\c&HEBE5FB&\3c&HB690F8&\bord2\blur3)\pos(440,407)}Operating   Room
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.47,0:06:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this... poison?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.10,0:06:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare an antidote!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.52,0:06:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Gaara...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.53,0:06:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Gaara...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.95,0:06:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Gaara was...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.46,0:06:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was having a bad feeling...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.17,0:06:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll take about two and a half days to get to the Sand from here...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.09,0:06:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.51,0:06:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.55,0:06:51.55,Title,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\shad0\fs34\fax0.08\bord0\frx20\fry346\frz15.744\t(27,1946,\fs31)\c&H90A2D7&\move(503,403,507,398,27,1946)}Treatment Room 3
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.59,0:06:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The wounds weren't that serious...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.47,0:06:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The problem is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.02,0:06:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The poison, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.73,0:07:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.52,0:07:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a completely new poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.44,0:07:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We have absolutely no idea how to neutralize it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.65,0:07:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Gaara... and now Kankuro, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.55,0:07:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Taking Naruto is the top-priority duty given to us by our organization, the Akatsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.06,0:07:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's not so much you that they're after...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.06,0:07:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...it's what's inside you they want.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.48,0:07:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But has long as you have the Nine-Tails sealed within you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.65,0:07:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...they might want to have that power under their own control...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.74,0:07:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto! I told you earlier not to disrupt the unit...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.52,0:08:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.00,0:08:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Even I know why they're after people like Gaara and me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.88,0:08:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You know it already, don't you, Sakura?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.60,0:08:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That I've got...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.68,0:08:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,...the Nine-Tailed Fox Spirit sealed inside me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.57,0:08:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey, it's that kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.99,0:08:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Eww, let's get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.58,0:08:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Gaara and I both... have monsters inside us...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.41,0:08:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what they're after!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.55,0:09:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I don't like!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.93,0:09:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,They only see us as monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.52,0:09:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like their selfish way of viewing us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.73,0:09:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A monster, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.98,0:09:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If that's the case, then we're the same...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.74,0:09:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was born a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.49,0:09:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything about us... was the same...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.75,0:09:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And he... fought all by himself a lot more than me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.17,0:09:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Naruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.26,0:09:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To them, I'm now an artifact of a past they want to erase.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.89,0:09:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then why should I exist and what should I live for?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.69,0:09:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I thought about it, but couldn't find an answer...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.52,0:09:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I need that reason while I'm alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.86,0:09:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If not, it's the same as dying...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.99,0:10:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The Akatsuki was after him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.00,0:10:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just like me this time, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.96,0:10:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet, why does he always have to be the one to get the short end of the stick?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.05,0:10:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's always him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.55,0:10:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I can't be wasting any time getting to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.80,0:10:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, I want to save him right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.15,0:10:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Naruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.62,0:10:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...Uzumaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.96,0:10:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.45,0:11:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You say Kankuro's regained consciousness?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.87,0:11:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He has, but he's just barely able to respond to us...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.20,0:11:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,His condition has worsened since yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.17,0:11:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,B-Baki... Is that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.47,0:11:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Kankuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.72,0:11:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's... it's him...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.68,0:11:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't raise your voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.22,0:11:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not good for you in your condition!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.81,0:11:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-The Red Sand...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.53,0:12:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... So that explains it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.07,0:12:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Baki...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.96,0:12:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Lord Baki.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.42,0:12:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Contact the tracking unit!\NTell them to turn back immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.80,0:12:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, we haven't heard anything from them since recovering Kankuro yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.88,0:12:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We were too late...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.30,0:12:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We have no choice but to consult with them...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.23,0:12:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.85,0:12:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing... I'm going out for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.94,0:12:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.61,0:12:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Our superiors told us to give them a progress report this morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.20,0:12:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think I have the time\Nto be leisurely giving reports?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.66,0:12:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Action takes precedence over meetings right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.49,0:12:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.79,0:12:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is what happens as soon as Gaara disappears...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.79,0:12:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Give me a break...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.92,0:13:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no choice but to consult with the honorable siblings...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.68,0:13:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But I wonder... will they come to our aid willingly?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.88,0:13:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, now, the food pills are only for emergencies...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.07,0:13:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Girls of your age especially need to be careful not to eat too...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.45,0:13:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,She got mad...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.29,0:13:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's totally sexual harassment... old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.21,0:13:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.04,0:13:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You've met him before, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.80,0:13:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Itachi Uchiha...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.72,0:13:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And he's after you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.89,0:13:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't just train over these past two and a half years.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.10,0:14:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I got into Master Tsunade's library and did outside investigations the best I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.23,0:14:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And now... what was bothering me finally makes sense now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.11,0:14:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wouldn't call it a dream, but I've got an ambition!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.62,0:14:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To restore the clan and to kill a certain man... no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.58,0:14:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm the only one who can kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.84,0:14:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm an avenger.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.88,0:14:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have to become stronger than him...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.76,0:14:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't have time to be getting tripped up in a place like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.56,0:14:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The person Sasuke wants to kill...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.35,0:14:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,...is his own older brother Itachi Uchiha, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.07,0:14:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,A member of the Akatsuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.45,0:14:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Itachi... Uchiha!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.45,0:14:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Itachi... Uchiha?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.58,0:14:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm going to kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.58,0:15:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just as you told me to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.38,0:15:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've resented you, hated you, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.72,0:15:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've lived...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.60,0:15:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've lived... only to kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.98,0:15:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sure enough, you're brothers...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.44,0:15:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see power greater than Itachi's hidden in those eyes of yours...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.12,0:15:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sasuke will definitely seek me out...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.12,0:15:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...in search of power...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.62,0:15:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why Sasuke is with Orochimaru in an attempt to obtain power...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.38,0:15:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But Orochimaru is after Sasuke's body, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.38,0:15:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And we only have six months left!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.72,0:15:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sakura knows about that too...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.18,0:16:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And Orochimaru used to be a member of the Akatsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.48,0:16:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Basically this is what I want... to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.11,0:16:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The closer we get to the Akatsuki,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.74,0:16:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,the closer we get to information about Orochimaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.28,0:16:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,If that happens...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.20,0:16:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,...we'll eventually get closer to Sasuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.96,0:16:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And after that, Itachi Uchiha...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.59,0:16:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Our worst enemy who plagued Sasuke for so long...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.76,0:16:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...and the one who's after Naruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.76,0:16:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This time I'll save the two of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.48,0:17:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It appears someone's come...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.52,0:17:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Big Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.24,0:17:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Big Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.85,0:18:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.83,0:18:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotcha! I was playing dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.00,0:18:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut it out. That senility act's too real, Big Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.47,0:18:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Honored siblings...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.94,0:18:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I have come to request your assistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.70,0:19:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Old books are supposed to be tied in a bundle and left up on a high shelf...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.87,0:19:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What can we possibly do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.62,0:19:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,An organization called the Akatsuki has taken the Shukaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.46,0:19:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If we leave things as they stand now, there will be great trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.09,0:19:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your generation now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.47,0:19:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys deal with it yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.30,0:19:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You two have powerful connections with each land,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.10,0:19:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,including villages in lands we are not allied with...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.23,0:19:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,There's only so much information we can gather on our own...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.02,0:19:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We've long since been retired.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.94,0:19:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We no longer have any attachments to the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.91,0:19:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Although I guess it'd be nice to see my grandchild's face one more time...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.79,0:19:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's very convenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.42,0:19:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Your grandson is a member of the Akatsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.18,0:20:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Granny Chiyo...
